001package edu.cnm.deepdive.gravity.model.entity;
002
003import androidx.annotation.NonNull;
004import androidx.room.ColumnInfo;
005import androidx.room.Entity;
006import androidx.room.Index;
007import androidx.room.PrimaryKey;
008import java.time.Instant;
009
010/**
011 * Encapsulates the data elements maintained for a signed-in user in the app's Room/SQLite-based
012 * persistent data store.
013 */
014@Entity(
015    tableName = "user",
016    indices = {
017        @Index(value = "oauth_key", unique = true),
018        @Index(value = "display_name", unique = true)
019    }
020)
021public class User {
022
023  @PrimaryKey(autoGenerate = true)
024  @ColumnInfo(name = "user_id")
025  private long id;
026
027  @NonNull
028  private Instant created = Instant.MIN;
029
030  @ColumnInfo(name = "oauth_key")
031  @NonNull
032  private String oauthKey = "";
033
034  @ColumnInfo(name = "display_name", collate = ColumnInfo.NOCASE)
035  @NonNull
036  private String displayName = "";
037
038  @ColumnInfo(name = "display_nick_name", collate = ColumnInfo.NOCASE)
039  @NonNull
040  private String displayNickName = "";
041
042  @ColumnInfo(name = "user_photo")
043  private String userPhoto = "";
044
045  public long getId() {
046    return id;
047  }
048
049  public void setId(long id) {
050    this.id = id;
051  }
052
053  @NonNull
054  public Instant getCreated() {
055    return created;
056  }
057
058  public void setCreated(@NonNull Instant created) {
059    this.created = created;
060  }
061
062  @NonNull
063  public String getOauthKey() {
064    return oauthKey;
065  }
066
067  public void setOauthKey(@NonNull String oauthKey) {
068    this.oauthKey = oauthKey;
069  }
070
071  @NonNull
072  public String getDisplayName() {
073    return displayName;
074  }
075
076  public void setDisplayName(@NonNull String displayName) {
077    this.displayName = displayName;
078  }
079
080  @NonNull
081  public String getDisplayNickName() {
082    return displayNickName;
083  }
084
085  public void setDisplayNickName(@NonNull String displayNickName) {
086    this.displayNickName = displayNickName;
087  }
088
089  public String getUserPhoto() {
090    return userPhoto;
091  }
092
093  public void setUserPhoto(String userPhoto) {
094    this.userPhoto = userPhoto;
095  }
096
097  @Override
098  public int hashCode() {
099    return Long.hashCode(id);
100  }
101
102}
103
